org.apache.openjpa.util

Class DelayedLinkedHashSetProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      • java.util.AbstractSet<E>
        • java.util.HashSet<E>
          • java.util.LinkedHashSet
            • org.apache.openjpa.util.DelayedLinkedHashSetProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable, Collection, Set, DelayedProxy, Proxy, ProxyCollection

    public class DelayedLinkedHashSetProxy
extends LinkedHashSet
implements DelayedProxy, ProxyCollection
    LinkedHashSet proxy with delay loading capability. Allows non-indexed add and remove operations to occur on an unloaded collection. Operations that require a load will trigger a load.
    See Also:
